Itâ€™s wearing an imperial war costume, reminding many viewers of classic monkey images. Nantou Mayor Sung Huai-lin says the design was created through discussion among city officials. After much deliberation, they wanted to throw out the serious and fierce looks of previous years, and go for a more light-hearted, fun and cheerful character. Sung Huai-lin Nantou mayor I want to report that this was designed by our colleague, a designer in the city hall. I hope the public can look for its positive aspects. Weâ€™d like to please everybody.
